# Optional developer fallback for the OpenAI API key.
#
# The primary way to set your key is in the app: Settings (gear) → OpenAI key.
# That value is stored in the OS app-config dir (not in this repo).
#
# If you prefer, you can instead drop the key here for local development — the
# Rust backend falls back to a process env var and then to this .env file when no
# key has been set in the app. Copy this file to `.env` and fill it in. NEVER
# commit `.env` (it is gitignored).
OPENAI_API_KEY=
